{{template "base/head" .}}
<div class="home">
	<div class="ui stackable middle very relaxed page grid">
		<div class="sixteen wide center aligned centered column">
			<div class="logo">
				<img src="{{AppSubUrl}}/img/favicon.png" />
			</div>
			<div class="hero">
				<h1 class="ui icon header title">
					AiicyDS
				</h1>
				<h2>{{.i18n.Tr "app_desc"}}</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	{{if eq .Lang "zh-CN"}}
		<div class="ui stackable middle very relaxed page grid">
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="desktop icon"></i> 易部署
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					您除了可以根据操作系统平台通过 <a target="_blank" href="https://aiicy.com/docs/installation/install_from_binary.html">二进制运行</a>，还可以通过 <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Aiicy/AiicyDS/tree/master/docker">Docker</a> 或 <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/geerlingguy/ansible-vagrant-examples/tree/master/AiicyDS">Vagrant</a>，以及 <a target="_blank" href="https://aiicy.com/docs/installation/install_from_packages.html">包管理</a> 安装。
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="cube icon"></i> 跨平台
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					任何 <a target="_blank" href="http://golang.org/">Go 语言</a> 支持的平台都可以运行 AiicyDS，包括 Windows、Mac、Linux 以及 ARM。
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ui stackable middle very relaxed page grid">
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="leaf icon"></i> 轻量级
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					一个廉价的树莓派的配置足以满足 AiicyDS 的最低系统硬件要求。最大程度上节省您的服务器资源！
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="puzzle icon"></i> 高度可定制
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					可高度自定义化的架构设计，一切尽在掌控。
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	{{else}}
		<div class="ui stackable middle very relaxed page grid">
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="desktop icon"></i> Easy to install
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					Simply <a target="_blank" href="https://aiicy.com/docs/installation/install_from_binary.html">run the binary</a> for your platform. Or ship AiicyDS with <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Aiicy/AiicyDS/tree/master/docker">Docker</a> or <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/geerlingguy/ansible-vagrant-examples/tree/master/AiicyDS">Vagrant</a>, or get it <a target="_blank" href="https://AiicyDS.io/docs/installation/install_from_packages.html">packaged</a>.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="cube icon"></i> Cross-platform
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					AiicyDS runs anywhere <a target="_blank" href="http://golang.org/">Go</a> can compile for: Windows, Mac OS X, Linux, ARM, etc.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="ui stackable middle very relaxed page grid">
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="leaf icon"></i> Lightweight
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					AiicyDS has low minimal requirements and can run on an inexpensive Raspberry Pi. Save your machine energy!
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="eight wide center column">
				<h1 class="hero ui icon header">
					<i class="puzzle icon"></i> Configurable
				</h1>
				<p class="large">
					Never mess up Git history with your customization again, be clean and well-organized.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	{{end}}
</div>
{{template "base/footer" .}}
